      "message": "I used std::string in video player to keep a buffer (based on your comments too), so make it to be consistent. Chromium src code uses std::string to keep unint8_t buffer in a lot of places. I can easily change to vector, of course.",
      "parentUuid": "62c81832_8da7c8ef",
