      "side": 1,
      "message": "(as in, silence from 0 ms to 49 ms, then real audio at 50 ms)\n\nThe user also doesn\u0027t necessarily have to wait while saving, since we also recently made the screen recording UI async.",
      "parentUuid": "57c285be_a074a6aa",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 536,
